{"title":"Migration of Hexo+Github Pages","date":"2020-03-10T07:30:11.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 10, 2020","L":"03/10/2020","MM-DD":"03-10"},"link":"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages","tags":["website"],"updated":"2020-03-10T07:36:38.976Z","content":"<p>Due to the novel coronavirus epidemic situation, I can’t go back to the laboratory  to update my website. Fortunately, I backed up the website data. I want to update the website through my pc.</p>\n<p>Here are my implementation steps.</p>\n<h2 id=\"1-Install-node-js\">1 Install node.js<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#1-Install-node-js\"></a></h2><h2 id=\"2-Install-Git\">2 Install Git<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#2-Install-Git\"></a></h2><h2 id=\"3-Install-hexo\">3 Install hexo<a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#3-Install-hexo\"></a></h2><blockquote>\n<p>Open cmd console, switch to :</p>\n<p>​    F:\\mywebsite\\blog</p>\n<p>And input this command, as below:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog&gt;npm install hexo-cli -g</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>initial your blog:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog&gt;hexo init thswind</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Warning: If your are failed, probably because of your internet speed is not good.</p>\n<p>Switch to thswind, and install some dependencies：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Install a deployer:</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight\"><div><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&gt; F:\\mywebsite\\blog\\thswind&gt;npm install hexo-deployer-git --save</span><br><span class=\"line\">&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></div></figure>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote>\n<h2 id=\"4-Migration\"><a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#4-Migration\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"4 Migration\"></a>4 Migration</h2><ol>\n<li>copy package.json package-lock.json from old pc to new pc</li>\n<li>copy thswind/source from old pc to thswind/source to new pc</li>\n<li>copy scaffolds to new pc</li>\n<li>copy themes to new pc</li>\n<li>copy blog\\thswind\\_config.yml to new pc</li>\n<li>copy thswind\\node_modules to new pc</li>\n</ol>\n<h2 id=\"Notes\"><a href=\"2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages#Notes\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Notes:\"></a>Notes:</h2><ol>\n<li>Maybe because of different os, there will be many warning and error information in cmd console. If you haven’t found a failed, then you can ignore it, or deal with it according to the tips.</li>\n</ol>\n</blockquote>\n","next":{"title":"math_formula_test","link":"2020/01/16/math-formula-test"},"plink":"https://thswind.github.io/2020/03/10/Migration-of-Hexo-Github-Pages/","toc":[{"title":"1 Install node.js","id":"1-Install-node-js","index":"1"},{"title":"2 Install Git","id":"2-Install-Git","index":"2"},{"title":"3 Install hexo","id":"3-Install-hexo","index":"3"},{"title":"","id":"4-Migration","index":"4"},{"title":"","id":"Notes","index":"5"}],"reward":true}